Hey :D
Here's another new map which comes with a lot of FUN! :D
It is a LEGO Packet Map with destructible LEGO-tiles.
There are many Pistols to use.

Shoot your way!!


How to install:
Just extract the aim_LegoOfDestruction_RoundTwo.bsp file into .../counter-strike: source/cstrike/maps/



Have Phun!! ;D
